snippet.title: James Cameron's Dark Angel - Gameplay Xbox HD 720P (Xbox to Xbox 360)
snippet.description:
Subscribe Now: http://goo.gl/21NQht
Visit us at http://www.godgames-world.com for more

How to play xbox 1 games on xbox 360: http://goo.gl/9dhXqa


James Cameron's Dark Angel is a video game for the PlayStation 2 and Xbox based on the television series Dark Angel (2000--2002). Developed by Radical Entertainment, the production was scaled back considerably following the cancellation of the show, and the game was met with both a critical and commercial scalding upon its release in 2002.


Played Xbox 1 on Xbox 360.For recording I used a Live Gamer HD Capture Card
*some games can have graphical issues, lags and other problems...
